---+TDWG 2008 Conference - Accomodation

In preparation for the TDWG 2008 conference in Fremantle, we have organised a listing of accomodation to suit a range of budgets.

---++Shared Apartments

Serviced Shared Apartments are some of the best options for quality, reasonably-priced accommodation around Fremantle. Each apartment comprises two or three bedrooms with common lounge, bathroom and sometimes kitchen facilities. 

We have looked for a range of apartments that are close to the conference venue and are good value.  While we cannot book them for you, we encourage delegates to indicate if they are looking for someone to share with.  Simply put your name under the apartments of your choice and leave your details so you can organise a group to share an apartment. _We will not be booking the apartments for you - the site is a meeting place for participants to come together and arrange a joint booking_

---+++Harbour Village Quest - [[http://www.harbourvillage.property.questwa.com.au/ Web site]] - [[http://www.harbourvillage.property.questwa.com.au/index.location.5220.html Map]]

These are serviced apartments.  The prices are:
   * $235 a night for a 2 bedroom apartment
   * $305 a night for a 3 bedroom apartment

There is a [[http://www.harbourvillage.property.questwa.com.au/ special booking page]] for TDWG 2008 attendees. At the bottom of the page, use the following Client login to book your accommodation:
   * User Name: QDEC
   * Password: hiabke

*Please nominate in the space below - with your contact email - if you are looking for someone to share this apartment with*



---+++The Westerley - [[http://www.fremantleharbourside.com.au/ Web Site]]

This offers short-term apartment rentals, with Harbourside Apartment prices of:

   * $175 a night for a Studio Apartment 
   * $225 a night for a 2 bedroom apartment
 
*Please nominate in the space below - with your contact email - if you are looking for someone to share this apartment with*




---+++Fremantle Colonial Accomodation - [[http://www.fremantlecolonialaccommodation.com.au/ Web site]]

This accomodation service offers a choice of rooms, apartments & cottages in central Fremantle & within the historic Fremantle Prison Grounds.  The prices are:

   * $150 a night for a single room 
   * $170 a night for a 2 bedroom apartment
   * $200 a night for a 2 bedroom cottage

*Please nominate in the space below - with your contact email - if you are looking for someone to share this apartment with*



---++Hotels

A range of hotels have also been put together for those preferring this accomodation.

---+++Esplanade Hotel - [[http://www.esplanadehotelfremantle.com.au/ Web site]]

The Esplanade is a 4.5 Star hotel.  If you mention the TDWG 2008 Conference, you will get the following prices:

   * $195.00 a night for a room

---+++Rosie O'Gradys - [[http://www.accommodation.rosieogradys.com.au/  Web site]]

Rosie's is an Irish Pub with Hotel accomodation in the middle of Fremantle.

   * $100 a night for a room

---+++Port Mill B&B - [[http://www.babs.com.au/portmill/ Web site]]

Port Mill is a Bed & Breakfast.  Prices are:

   * $170 - $190 per night including full breakfast - and if you stay 6 nights, you get 1 night free 

---++Other

If none of these suit your requirements, we recommend that you look at the following web sites for something that suits you.

   * [[http://www.freofocus.com/dbtext/html/accommodation.asp FreoFocus]] - Web site maintained by City of Freo
   * [[http://www.fremantlewa.com.au/ Fremantle WA]] - Web site for Fremantle accomodation
   * [[http://www.wotif.com.au/ Wotif]] - Last minute style booking service (useful for testing prices!)
   * [[http://www.ratestogo.com.au Ratestogo]] - Last minute style booking service (useful for testing prices!)
@


